[To] Ferryd Shillor

[NPC Internal] Here are the two wands you requested as proof.
[NPC] Ferryd: You will soon no longer be just an Apprentice of the Red Way, though you still have a long journey ahead of you.
[NPC] Ferryd: Never think you know all there is to know either.
[NPC] Ferryd: That is the path to folly, and I will be sure to trip you on the way.
[NPC Narrate] -Ferryd hands back one wand with a friendly grin.-
[NPC] Ferryd: Return this to your fellow student.
[NPC] Ferryd: Your new wand will be ready soon.
[NPC] Ferryd: We will be spending quite a bit of time together over the next weeks, and I am an easy man to get along with as long as you don't take yourself too seriously.
